    Frequently Asked Questions

    What’s included in the package?

    • 1 TinyThinkers™ Magic Workbook
    • 1 Disappearing Ink Pen
    • 6 Ink Refills

    How does the workbook help in my child’s development?

    This workbook focuses on nurturing essential skills, including pattern and color recognition, fine motor skills, concentration, and hand-eye coordination. These areas are crucial for the well-rounded development of young learners, aiding in their cognitive and physical growth.

    Is this suitable for my child’s age?

    Yes! It’s designed for kids aged 3–8, helping them develop fine motor skills, letter formation, and pen control.

    Are the materials used in the workbook safe for children?

    Yes, the workbook is crafted with non-toxic materials, prioritizing the safety and well-being of children. Parents and caregivers can have peace of mind knowing that the workbook is safe for young learners to use.

    Does this actually improve handwriting?

    Yes! The combination of guided grooves, repetition, and fading ink encourages proper letter formation, improving writing skills faster than traditional workbooks.
